messages.content:
This is a missed-optimization in GVN.

The following program reveals the missed optimization.
The source program is
```llvm
define i1 @not_cond_logic1(i1 %c, i1 %d) {
  %c.not = xor i1 %c, true
  %and = and i1 %c.not, %d
  br i1 %and, label %if, label %else

if:                                               ; preds = %0
  ret i1 %c

else:                                             ; preds = %0
  ret i1 %c
}

```

However, current LLVM cannot optimize the source program. The expected optimized program is
```llvm
define i1 @not_cond_logic1(i1 %c, i1 %d) {
  %c.not = xor i1 %c, true
  %and = and i1 %c.not, %d
  br i1 %and, label %if, label %else

if:                                               ; preds = %0
  ret i1 false

else:                                             ; preds = %0
  ret i1 %c
}

```
Please modify the following code in llvm/lib/Transforms/Scalar/GVN.cpp:GVNPass::propagateEquality to implement the missed optimization:
```cpp
      if (RootDominatesEnd)
